=== Introduction ===
twicli <http://www.geocities.jp/twicli/twicli.html> is a browser based twitter
client that was originally developed by NeoCat <http://twitter.com/NeoCat>.

I, edvakf <http://my.opera.com/edvakf/blog/>, ported it to Opera Unite.
The main part of twicli is almost not modified at all.
What I did was to make a twicli plugin, operaunite.js, and the server side
caching mechanizm.

This is not a fork of the original Twicli, so when the original is updated,
all you need to do to be up-to-date is to download the files from the 
repository <http://coderepos.org/share/browser/websites/twicli/> and put
them into the "public_html" directory.


=== Diff between the original twicli and twicli Unite ===

% diff -u twicli_orig.html twicli.html
--- twicli_orig.html	2009-07-28 15:19:37.000000000 -0400
+++ twicli.html	2009-08-22 03:56:23.000000000 -0400
@@ -279,7 +279,7 @@
 var twitterURL = 'http://twitter.com/';
 var cookieVer = parseInt(readCookie('ver')) || 0;
 var updateInterval = (cookieVer>3) && parseInt(readCookie('update_interval')) || 60;
-var pluginstr = (cookieVer>5) && readCookie('tw_plugins') || ' regexp.js\noutputz.js\nsearch.js\nsearch2.js\nfavotter.js\nfollowers.js';
+var pluginstr = (cookieVer>5) && readCookie('tw_plugins') || ' operaunite.js\nregexp.js\noutputz.js\nsearch.js\nsearch2.js\nfavotter.js\nfollowers.js';
 pluginstr = pluginstr.substr(1);
 var nr_limit = parseInt(readCookie('limit')) || 500;				// 表示する発言数の上限
 var max_count = (cookieVer>3) && parseInt(readCookie('max_count')) || 50;

